Secondary Cancer Disorder

Types of secondary malignant neoplastic disease, coded in SNOMED CT. Use a code from the disorder hierarchy under secondary malignant neoplastic disease (SNOMED CT 128462008).

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include codes from http://snomed.info/sct where concept is-a 128462008
